https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500null Through the power of imagination, Barney takes BJ, Baby Bop, Rachel and Jackson to visit a real farm! Once there, they get a chance to see how crops are grown and how real animals are taken care of. They also meet Farmer Dooley and his wife, who involve them in a varety of fun activities - including preparing for a big barn dance. Barney: Let's Go To The Farm
